### Tags ###
# Ignore tags created by etags, ctags, gtags (GNU global) and cscope
TAGS
.TAGS
!TAGS/
tags
.tags
!tags/
gtags.files
GTAGS
GRTAGS
GPATH
GSYMS
cscope.files
cscope.out
cscope.in.out
cscope.po.out


# End of https://www.toptal.com/developers/gitignore/api/tags
